Introduction

Bolbbalgan4 (Bolbbalgan Sachungi, also known as Blushing Youth, Bolppalgan Puberty or BOL4) is formerly a South Korean duo formed by Shofar Music in 2016. Before signing with their current agency the duo participated in Superstar K6 in 2014. On April 2, 2020, it was announced that Woo Jiyoon would be leaving the duo and Ahn Jiyoung would be promoting solo as Bolbbalgan4.
